No DNA, nothing at all.

00:29:12.465 --> 00:29:15.185
We can only tell
it's been there a long time.

00:29:17.864 --> 00:29:23.344
The victim bought the resale property
when marrying four years ago.

00:29:24.104 --> 00:29:26.425
The suspect's been watching the victim
that long?

