If that's the case,

00:29:29.265 --> 00:29:33.985
we can exclude who Wang Xiaole and Wu Da
met in the last four years, right?

00:29:35.905 --> 00:29:41.496
No fingerprints besides those of Wu Da,
Wang Xiaole, Huang Chong,

00:29:41.752 --> 00:29:45.064
or the victim's parents
are found at the scene.

00:29:47.344 --> 00:29:48.665
DNA

00:29:50.265 --> 00:29:51.928
suggests the killer

00:29:54.392 --> 00:29:59.985
didn't have time to clean yet.

00:30:16.248 --> 00:30:19.544
(Wu Da)

00:30:20.945 --> 00:30:22.584
I won't finish early today.

00:30:22.584 --> 00:30:23.584
Don't wait for me.

00:30:25.505 --> 00:30:26.185
By the way,

00:30:26.425 --> 00:30:28.505
I ordered some vegetable racks online.

00:30:28.505 --> 00:30:29.945
Should arrive in a few days.

