Captain Leng,

00:30:50.864 --> 00:30:55.384
I found no valuable clues
at the south gate.

00:30:55.985 --> 00:30:56.584
Right.

00:30:57.344 --> 00:31:00.384
Same for the woods
outside the north gate.

00:31:01.185 --> 00:31:02.665
Too little useful evidence.

00:31:02.665 --> 00:31:03.985
I'm still looking.

00:31:06.708 --> 00:31:12.185
(Yunxi Medical University)

00:31:12.185 --> 00:31:12.945
Ye,

00:31:13.304 --> 00:31:14.985
sorry to keep you waiting.

00:31:15.104 --> 00:31:17.225
(File Bag)
Look, these old files

00:31:17.465 --> 00:31:19.824
are stored
in the old teaching building's archive.

00:31:20.185 --> 00:31:22.784
We haven't digitized them yet.

00:31:23.064 --> 00:31:24.425
Hence the delay.

00:31:24.905 --> 00:31:26.384
You're too kind, Mr. Liu.

00:31:26.705 --> 00:31:28.784
I should thank you
for assisting our investigation.

00:31:29.265 --> 00:31:30.384
(Graduate Registration Form)
My pleasure.

00:31:30.384 --> 00:31:31.425
You may not know.

00:31:31.784 --> 00:31:36.384
I was Wu Da and Xiaole's
homeroom teacher.

00:31:38.025 --> 00:31:41.025
When Wu Da applied
to transfer departments,

00:31:41.064 --> 00:31:43.304
(Wu Da's Profile)
I advised him not to act impulsively.

00:31:44.225 --> 00:31:46.344
Ours is a top university.

00:31:46.544 --> 00:31:48.705
Getting into our department isn't easy.

00:31:49.465 --> 00:31:52.304
I advised him
to cherish this opportunity.

00:31:52.304 --> 00:31:55.025
But he refused on the spot.

00:31:55.265 --> 00:31:59.584
He even said he wasn't cut out
for medicine at all,

00:31:59.985 --> 00:32:04.344
and Xiaole was the only reason
he chose clinical.

00:32:04.864 --> 00:32:05.705
- That kid...
- Sir,

00:32:06.104 --> 00:32:07.945
based on your understanding of Wu Da,

00:32:08.425 --> 00:32:11.225
could he achieve such precision
with the incision?

00:32:11.225 --> 00:32:11.824
Wu Da?

00:32:12.104 --> 00:32:15.265
He couldn't hold the scalpel properly
during training.

00:32:15.425 --> 00:32:16.505
This photo

00:32:16.624 --> 00:32:19.064
shows a clean, neat incision

00:32:19.225 --> 00:32:20.265
with perfectly even force.

00:32:20.465 --> 00:32:23.265
Without years of practice
and solid fundamentals,

00:32:23.465 --> 00:32:24.784
one simply couldn't have done it.

00:32:29.544 --> 00:32:30.144
Sir,

00:32:31.225 --> 00:32:34.824
Wu Da received a disciplinary demerit
while at school?

00:32:36.745 --> 00:32:39.624
It was for fighting
with another student.

00:32:39.824 --> 00:32:42.384
The kids acted impulsively,

00:32:42.864 --> 00:32:46.025
but actually,
they were very close friends.

00:32:46.104 --> 00:32:48.705
They were inseparable all day long.

00:32:55.304 --> 00:32:55.985
Ye,

00:32:56.624 --> 00:32:58.465
how are your parents doing overseas?

00:33:00.384 --> 00:33:01.185
They're doing fine.

00:33:02.265 --> 00:33:04.265
When you talk to them next time,

00:33:04.384 --> 00:33:07.104
tell them
we old friends still think of them.

00:33:07.584 --> 00:33:08.784
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

00:33:09.185 --> 00:33:09.784
By the way,

00:33:10.104 --> 00:33:12.384
could you please help me find out

00:33:12.384 --> 00:33:14.784
the specific details
of Wu Da's fight and demerit?

00:33:15.025 --> 00:33:18.185
No problem. I'll tell you
as soon as I find anything.

00:33:18.265 --> 00:33:18.864
Thank you.

00:33:19.144 --> 00:33:20.104
Take care. I'm off.

00:33:20.104 --> 00:33:21.624
Alright, take care.

00:33:37.505 --> 00:33:41.425
I went to a movie
with Little Zhao that day.

00:33:45.225 --> 00:33:46.745
But I used your name to invite her.

00:33:46.905 --> 00:33:48.265
You don't mind, do you?

00:33:51.025 --> 00:33:52.425
Can't you rely on yourself?

00:33:52.665 --> 00:33:54.144
I do want to rely on myself, bro.

00:33:54.144 --> 00:33:55.544
But I can't get her out like that.

00:33:55.544 --> 00:33:56.384
She won't come.

00:34:01.624 --> 00:34:02.784
Just tell me,

00:34:02.985 --> 00:34:06.784
is there even the slightest chance
between you two?

00:34:07.185 --> 00:34:08.064
There isn't.

00:34:08.064 --> 00:34:09.825
Okay then, that puts my mind at ease.

00:34:10.064 --> 00:34:13.104
Actually, the atmosphere
during the movie was pretty good.

00:34:14.144 --> 00:34:15.064
It looked promising.

00:34:15.224 --> 00:34:18.025
But unfortunately,
I had to leave halfway through.

00:34:28.345 --> 00:34:30.584
How about doing another favor for me?

00:34:31.744 --> 00:34:32.584
What now?

00:34:33.985 --> 00:34:35.945
I invited Little Zhao
for a late-night snack.

00:34:35.945 --> 00:34:36.785
I said you'll go too.

00:34:36.785 --> 00:34:38.785
And she just replied, saying yes.

00:34:43.192 --> 00:34:46.985
(No-Name Diner)

00:34:46.985 --> 00:34:47.785
Jing.

00:34:48.624 --> 00:34:50.624
You're here. Perfect, it's all ready.

00:34:50.624 --> 00:34:51.104
Great.

00:34:51.104 --> 00:34:51.744
Dig in.

00:34:51.744 --> 00:34:52.505
- Thanks.
- Jing.

00:34:52.985 --> 00:34:53.752
Here, Little Zhao.

00:34:53.905 --> 00:34:54.945
Is she your girlfriend?

00:34:54.945 --> 00:34:55.544
A friend.

