- No.
- Not my girlfriend.

00:34:57.064 --> 00:34:58.144
- Sit.
- Eat up.

00:34:58.144 --> 00:34:59.305
Holler if you need me.

00:34:59.305 --> 00:35:00.264
Got it.

00:35:01.264 --> 00:35:03.825
So this is the amazing restaurant
you keep mentioning?

00:35:04.184 --> 00:35:05.785
The place looks pretty ordinary.

00:35:06.305 --> 00:35:08.184
And the dishes
seem like regular home cooking.

00:35:09.505 --> 00:35:10.544
Let me try this.

00:35:11.465 --> 00:35:12.385
That's delicious.

00:35:13.544 --> 00:35:14.785
I think it's quite tasty.

00:35:14.785 --> 00:35:15.785
Better than my cooking.

00:35:16.584 --> 00:35:17.345
It's good.

00:35:17.664 --> 00:35:18.985
If you say it's good, then it is.

00:35:23.785 --> 00:35:24.465
Tasty.

00:35:36.144 --> 00:35:37.264
Captain Qin, you're here.

00:35:37.264 --> 00:35:37.905
Is it ready?

00:35:37.905 --> 00:35:38.664
All ready.

00:35:38.664 --> 00:35:39.624
Come on in and sit down.

00:35:39.624 --> 00:35:41.505
I'll serve the noodles right away.
Just sit.

00:35:41.624 --> 00:35:42.425
- Okay.
- Right away.

00:35:42.425 --> 00:35:43.144
- Jing.
- Come on.

00:35:44.144 --> 00:35:44.865
What's going on?

00:35:44.865 --> 00:35:46.104
Serve the noodles, Shan.

00:35:46.624 --> 00:35:47.264
Qian.

00:35:48.744 --> 00:35:49.224
Long.

00:35:49.224 --> 00:35:50.025
Serve the noodles.

00:35:50.025 --> 00:35:50.985
Long, you're here too.

00:35:51.104 --> 00:35:51.664
You're here.

00:35:51.664 --> 00:35:52.184
Enjoy.

00:35:52.184 --> 00:35:53.465
Qian and Long, you're here too.

00:35:54.584 --> 00:35:56.025
- You're here.
- You must be starving.

00:35:56.025 --> 00:35:56.704
Eat your food.

00:35:56.704 --> 00:35:57.305
Here.

00:35:57.945 --> 00:35:59.104
- Free noodles.
- Qian. Long.

00:35:59.104 --> 00:35:59.704
Come on.

00:36:00.184 --> 00:36:01.305
Everyone, eat up.

00:36:02.465 --> 00:36:03.385
- Noodles.
- Serve this table.

00:36:03.584 --> 00:36:04.144
Here.

00:36:04.144 --> 00:36:04.825
Coming right up.

00:36:09.144 --> 00:36:09.744
Here.

00:36:11.025 --> 00:36:12.184
Give this to them first.

00:36:15.064 --> 00:36:16.704
How about we find another place?

00:36:17.184 --> 00:36:17.985
What's wrong?

00:36:18.825 --> 00:36:23.025
I feel creeped out even though
I haven't done anything wrong.

00:36:23.025 --> 00:36:23.905
It's no big deal.

00:36:23.905 --> 00:36:25.144
They're the Public Order Unit.

00:36:25.624 --> 00:36:26.505
The power of justice.

00:36:26.825 --> 00:36:28.465
There must be another operation tonight.

00:36:29.704 --> 00:36:30.584
There's an operation?

00:36:44.345 --> 00:36:45.385
(Team One, Team One.)

00:36:45.385 --> 00:36:46.664
(Team Two, Team Two, move out.)

00:36:47.064 --> 00:36:47.905
Copy. Moving out.

00:36:48.025 --> 00:36:48.945
- Copy that.
- Copy that.

00:36:48.945 --> 00:36:49.465
- Copy that.
- Move.

00:36:49.465 --> 00:36:49.985
Let's go.

00:36:49.985 --> 00:36:50.744
Let's go.

00:36:51.025 --> 00:36:52.184
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

00:37:22.584 --> 00:37:23.865
What's happening tonight?

00:37:23.865 --> 00:37:24.865
Why the rush?

00:37:26.305 --> 00:37:27.345
Liu and Shan, come here.

00:37:28.184 --> 00:37:28.905
Clean those up.

00:37:28.905 --> 00:37:30.425
They probably won't be back soon.

00:37:31.624 --> 00:37:32.465
Grab that bucket.

00:37:32.945 --> 00:37:35.785
Pour everything into the bucket

00:37:36.224 --> 00:37:38.505
for the stray cats, dogs, and such.

00:37:39.425 --> 00:37:40.264
Look at them.

00:37:40.385 --> 00:37:41.624
Put it on the table for now.

00:37:48.345 --> 00:37:49.224
- Hello, Master.
- Hello, Lei.

00:37:53.345 --> 00:37:53.985
Coming.

00:37:54.680 --> 00:37:58.232
(No-Name Diner)

00:38:03.144 --> 00:38:04.584
What's going on tonight?

00:38:07.505 --> 00:38:08.305
Just sit.

00:38:10.184 --> 00:38:11.465
You'll get used to it.

00:38:12.905 --> 00:38:15.664
That's the nature of their job.
They leave at a moment's notice.

00:38:17.945 --> 00:38:19.264
How about I join you?

00:38:19.465 --> 00:38:20.664
Or it'll all go to waste.

00:38:20.664 --> 00:38:21.345
Okay.

00:38:21.865 --> 00:38:22.664
Let's eat.

00:38:26.465 --> 00:38:27.264
Ms. Jing,

00:38:28.744 --> 00:38:30.905
does Ye Qian come here often?

00:38:32.544 --> 00:38:33.505
He comes often.

00:38:37.584 --> 00:38:42.264
Has he brought other girls here before?

00:38:45.025 --> 00:38:47.985
Anyway, you're the first girl
they've brought here.

00:38:54.945 --> 00:38:55.505
Ms. Jing,

00:38:56.144 --> 00:38:58.584
is your family in the same line of work?

00:39:00.544 --> 00:39:03.025
My husband, Jiao Lei,
is their colleague.

00:39:03.025 --> 00:39:03.985
He's also a cop.

00:39:05.865 --> 00:39:07.184
My son used to be a soldier.

00:39:07.425 --> 00:39:08.465
A border guard.

00:39:09.064 --> 00:39:09.865
That's cool.

00:39:10.825 --> 00:39:12.224
Quite a handsome young man.

00:39:13.224 --> 00:39:14.664
Lots of girls liked him.

00:39:18.985 --> 00:39:20.905
But he died on duty five years ago.

00:39:24.624 --> 00:39:26.704
I've worked in food service
since before my son.

00:39:28.224 --> 00:39:30.025
I wanted to open my own restaurant

00:39:30.785 --> 00:39:32.025
to honor my son

00:39:32.305 --> 00:39:34.064
and keep myself occupied.

00:39:35.425 --> 00:39:38.985
Jiao's unit was setting up a canteen
for field personnel back then,

00:39:39.465 --> 00:39:41.064
and the leaders sympathized with me,

00:39:41.345 --> 00:39:42.744
so they gave us priority

00:39:43.104 --> 00:39:44.345
and hence this restaurant.

00:39:45.465 --> 00:39:48.144
We sometimes provide meals
for sanitation workers.

00:39:48.264 --> 00:39:49.465
It's volunteer-based too.

00:39:54.465 --> 00:39:55.945
People need something to hold onto.

00:39:56.785 --> 00:39:58.785
It feels good to do something
for that purpose.

00:39:59.624 --> 00:40:02.704
Can I come help next time then?

00:40:04.144 --> 00:40:05.184
Of course.

00:40:06.144 --> 00:40:06.785
You're welcome.

00:40:06.985 --> 00:40:07.785
Alright.

00:40:08.744 --> 00:40:09.544
Eat more.

00:40:11.744 --> 00:40:12.544
You eat too.

00:40:14.825 --> 00:40:15.505
Slow down.

00:40:43.544 --> 00:40:45.785
Is this the old chemical factory's
discharge pool?

00:40:46.064 --> 00:40:47.305
Why the strong smell?

00:40:48.704 --> 00:40:52.744
This whole area
used to be a chemical factory.

00:40:53.184 --> 00:40:55.064
Later, the factory relocated.
The land was sold.

00:40:55.064 --> 00:40:56.544
It's been left abandoned ever since.

00:40:56.664 --> 00:40:59.025
Now it's entirely a garbage dump.

00:40:59.584 --> 00:41:01.385
If it hadn't become a dump,

00:41:01.584 --> 00:41:03.224
I wouldn't have found this place.

00:41:04.985 --> 00:41:06.144
See that surveillance camera?

00:41:07.664 --> 00:41:10.584
Coming through the woods,
there's only this one camera.

00:41:11.025 --> 00:41:12.425
The camera was installed

00:41:12.425 --> 00:41:16.905
by the city sanitation department
to catch trucks illegally dumping trash.

